{"tid":2190851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭:普檢反應正面 超過9成按預約前往 人數破百萬","createTime":"2020-09-06T04:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T10:10:16.000Z","uid":137088,"like":7,"dislike":362,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcf7d5a9723d346b46ce9568f8fe52170b9f1eb","tid":2190851,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網頁說，登記人數突破100萬，5日以來有85萬名市民到各個的檢測中心接受採樣，普遍反應很正面，網上登記的市民有超過9成都有按照預約時間前往中心，完成採樣的人士之中，有大約18%是在現場登記。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，早前有意見質疑有人重複檢測，但實際情況是重複檢測的只有幾百宗，可能是個別市民認為有需要再次檢測，例如首次檢測後接觸高危群組，或者是有人想測試系統，但對整體數字的影響微不足道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548072-20200905.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548072-20200905.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=813c1cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548072-20200905.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b635ffc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548072-20200905.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4a3f79402e88f6a77ba2f6537b03e631aefa3650","tid":2190851,"uid":30113,"like":322,"dislike":3,"score":319,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾  有600百幾萬杯葛又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7be734bb1224e8bc5509e52277c6b273d83c64","tid":2190851,"uid":155095,"like":59,"dislike":5,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"4a3f79402e88f6a77ba2f6537b03e631aefa3650","tid":2190851,"uid":30113,"like":322,"dislike":3,"score":319,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾  有600百幾萬杯葛又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"港共：超過民主派初選人數就